{"id": 57868, "date": "2025-07-28T04:00:35", "date_gmt": "2025-07-28T11:00:35", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57868"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T12:07:15", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T19:07:15", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-28-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/28/kingdom-of-days-july-28-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 28"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1944:\u00a0</strong>Bobby King, backing vocalist on &#8220;Roll of the Dice&#8221; and &#8220;Man&#8217;s Job&#8221; and throughout World Tour 1992 and World Tour 1993, is born in Lake Charles, Louisiana.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3227\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/bobby/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/bobby.jpg?fit=420%2C420&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"420,420\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"bobby\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/bobby.jpg?fit=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/bobby.jpg?fit=420%2C420&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3227 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/bobby.jpg?resize=420%2C420&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"420\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/bobby.jpg?w=420&amp;ssl=1 420w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/bobby.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/bobby.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/bobby.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1966:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles participate in Asbury Park&#8217;s first annual Rock&#8217;n&#8217;Roll Contest, where first prize is awarded to The Shadows, featuring Steven Van Zandt.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"52813\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/asbury_park_press_1966_08_05_page_21/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Asbury_Park_Press_1966_08_05_Page_21.jpg?fit=%2C&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"[]\" data-image-title=\"Asbury_Park_Press_1966_08_05_Page_21\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Asbury_Park_Press_1966_08_05_Page_21.jpg?fit=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Asbury_Park_Press_1966_08_05_Page_21.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-52813 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Asbury_Park_Press_1966_08_05_Page_21.jpg?resize=758%2C722&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"722\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play a show at the Tucson Community Center.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"52814\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/tucson_citizen_1974_07_26_19/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?fit=1622%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1622,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?fit=190%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?fit=649%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-52814 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C1196&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1196\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?w=1622&amp;ssl=1 1622w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?resize=190%2C300&amp;ssl=1 190w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?resize=649%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 649w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1212&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?resize=973%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 973w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Tucson_Citizen_1974_07_26_19-scaled.jpg?w=1516&amp;ssl=1 1516w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"36103\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-0728-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1974-0728.jpg?fit=202%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"202,300\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-0728\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1974-0728.jpg?fit=202%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1974-0728.jpg?fit=202%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-36103 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/1974-0728.jpg?resize=202%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"202\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>A rainy night plagues Bruce&#8217;s performance at the Carter Barron Amphitheater in Washington DC&#8217;s Rock Creek Park. Heavy rain delays the start of the show by two hours, and lingering moisture disrupts Bruce&#8217;s guitar throughout the show, causing additional mid-show delays. Still, the performance is great, and the crowd is hot. Listen to the rare instrumental &#8220;Funk Song&#8221; below.</p>\n<div id=\"v-PjwQpbMI-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/PjwQpbMI?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1SF6X8x3aEw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RD1SF6X8x3aEw\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce&#8217;s cover of &#8220;Summertime Blues&#8221; makes its debut in his Darkness Tour show in Miami.</p>\n<div id=\"v-9mruPo23-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/9mruPo23?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28489\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-07-28b-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-28b.png?fit=794%2C3415&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"794,3415\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aper